<title>USA: Autotote loss narrows,1995 includes charges.</title>
<headline>Autotote loss narrows,1995 includes charges.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1996-08-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>1996			1995</p>
<p> Shr loss		   $0.25     loss	 $1.01</p>
<p> Net loss		   7,804     loss	29,246</p>
<p> Revs			41,828		   38,722</p>
<p> Avg shrs		  31,459		   28,928</p>
<p>	   9 MONTHS</p>
<p> Shr loss		   $0.88     loss	 $1.53</p>
<p> Net loss		  27,499     loss	44,135</p>
<p> Revs		     130,875		  106,971</p>
<p> Avg shrs		  31,246		   28,884</p>
<p>(All data above 000s except per share numbers)</p>
<p>NOTE: 1995 both periods include a restructuring charge of $11.6 million, and a write-off of investments amounting to $6.6 million.</p>
<p>Q3 1996 include two unusual charges of $647,000 - related to an incomplete debt offering - and $569,000 for contractual payments.  These were partially offset by a reversal of $649,000 in 1995 restructuring cost accruals.</p>
<p>Full company name is Autotote Corp.</p>
<p>---New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610</p>
